Package: ggplot3scene
Type: Package
Title: Prototype Scene3D Compiler for R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("ggplot3scene", "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "noreply@example.com")
Author: ggplot3scene contributors
Maintainer: ggplot3scene contributors <noreply@example.com>
Description: Builds language-neutral Scene3D JSON documents from R data and
    exports interactive HTML previews plus fixed-size figure outputs for
    prototype three-dimensional scientific plots.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: jsonlite, htmltools
Suggests: testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
License: MIT
